metadata.name: Orange is the new Black
metadata.description:
Meet Don, a successful businessman from the glamorous era of the 1960s, residing in the bustling city of Los Angeles. Don is a man of exquisite taste, always dressed in sharp suits and driving his beloved Porsche 911 through the bustling streets of the city. He exudes an air of confidence and sophistication, with his slicked-back hair and a classic cigarette in hand. With his charming demeanor and quick wit, Don has made a name for himself in the business world, with many considering him to be a true trailblazer in his field. 

His ambition and unwavering determination have helped him achieve great success, but his true passion lies in the thrill of the chase - whether it be sealing a lucrative business deal or taking a winding road in his sleek sports car.

Don is a man of many talents, and there's no telling where his next adventure will take him. Here we see him driving towards the garage door of one of his many homes.
